{"tid":1768254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再喺Telegram公海講私密嘢","createTime":"2019-12-04T02:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T04:52:01.000Z","uid":66049,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"174fb40758ef9d31f217e1cb0d7a8d2de5df0861","tid":1768254,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"近排搵到個鄰國朋友傾計<br />\n問佢地點樣搵到香港Telegram公海<br />\n佢就推介呢個bot俾我<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">@hao1234bot</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n聽到<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">hao123</span></span></strong>都知唔慌係好嘢<br />\n結果用vpn開嚟睇下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">嘩屌你老母真係乜撚公海channel都有</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係唔該你地唔好再喺Telegram組織行動做犯法嘢<br />\n啲Mon Post狗肯定入咗去同我地一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔撚想知你發夢做過啲乜嘢</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CCnzzKF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCCnzzKF.png&h=9a0c6509&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ce7GZbm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCe7GZbm.png&h=0ea8de8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VY5YgX3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVY5YgX3.png&h=077f0b38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yPCsah4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyPCsah4.png&h=9db48735&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fNbsUKL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfNbsUKL.png&h=c5362453&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qa5GpM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3